ined by Tom Holland, manages to get Spidey’s first feature film in the Marvel Cinematic Universe right. His performance, both as Peter Parker and Spiderman, suits him perfectly. The plot itself manages to fit right into Marvel’s universe with the help of Robert Downey Jr.’s Tony Stark character mentoring Peter Parker. At the same time, the entire supporting cast exhibited a strong performance, especially Michael Keaton’s Adrian Toomes, or the Vulture.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-166\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Is-The-New-Spiderman-Movie-Any-Good_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">All in all, Spiderman: Homecoming takes everyone’s expectations and launches it to the stars. This is mainly because of a compelling plot, brilliant performances, and its amazing ties to the MCU.</h4>','Is The New Spiderman Movie Any Good?','','publish','closed','closed','','is-the-new-spiderman-movie-any-good','','','2017-07-08 16:21:37','2017-07-08 16:21:37','',0,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/?p=164',0,'post','',0),(165,1,'2017-07-08 16:17:03','2017-07-08 16:17:03','','Is The New Spiderman Movie Any Good_01','','inherit','closed','closed','','is-the-new-spiderman-movie-any-good_01','','','2017-07-08 16:17:03','2017-07-08 16:17:03','',164,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Is-The-New-Spiderman-Movie-Any-Good_01.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(166,1,'2017-07-08 16:17:05','2017-07-08 16:17:05','','Is The New Spiderman Movie Any Good_02','','inherit','closed','closed','','is-the-new-spiderman-movie-any-good_02','','','2017-07-08 16:17:05','2017-07-08 16:17:05','',164,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Is-The-New-Spiderman-Movie-Any-Good_02.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(167,1,'2017-07-08 16:17:40','2017-07-08 16:17:40','<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chances are, Spiderman: Homecoming is showing in a theater near you. After five movies and a couple of animated series, most people are wondering if the new Spiderman movie is worth all the hype.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-165\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Is-The-New-Spiderman-Movie-Any-Good_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"709\" height=\"532\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The good news is yes, it most certainly does. The movie, headlined by Tom Holland, manages to get Spidey’s first feature film in the Marvel Cinematic Universe right. His performance, both as Peter Parker and Spiderman, suits him perfectly. The plot itself manages to fit right into Marvel’s universe with the help of Robert Downey Jr.’s Tony Stark character mentoring Peter Parker. At the same time, the entire supporting cast exhibited a strong performance, especially Michael Keaton’s Adrian Toomes, or the Vulture.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-166\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Is-The-New-Spiderman-Movie-Any-Good_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">All in all, Spiderman: Homecoming takes everyone’s expectations and launches it to the stars. This is mainly because of a compelling plot, brilliant performances, and its amazing ties to the MCU.</h4>','Is The New Spiderman Movie Any Good?','','inherit','closed','closed','','164-revision-v1','','','2017-07-08 16:17:40','2017-07-08 16:17:40','',164,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/164-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(168,1,'2017-07-08 16:19:35','2017-07-08 16:19:35','<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hold your horses and forget everything you knew about Amelia Earhart’s disappearance in 1937. A new photograph has emerged and it could suggest Earhart and navigator Fred Noonan survived their plane crash and ended up in the Marshall Islands.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-170\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Photograph-about-how-Amelia-Earhart-ended-up-in-the-Marshall-Islands-surfaces_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The photo, obtained from the National Archives by a retired federal agent named Les Kinney, shows a woman with a strong resemblance to Earhart, sitting with her back to the camera. There’s also a man in the leftmost side of the photo who is believed to be Noonan. Along with Earhart and Noonan, there are also a couple of local citizens in a dock with a Japanese vessel in the background.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-169\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Photograph-about-how-Amelia-Earhart-ended-up-in-the-Marshall-Islands-surfaces_00.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a documentary about this new discovery, Forensic analyst Kent Gibson confirmed that the Japanese ship is the Koshu Maru, an army vessel. He also said that the man and woman in the photo exhibit strong features of Earhart and Noonan.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">If confirmed, this changes a lot about how these two disappeared during the late 30s.</h4>','Photograph about how Amelia Earhart ended up in the Marshall Islands surfaces','','publish','closed','closed','','photograph-about-how-amelia-earhart-ended-up-in-the-marshall-islands-surfaces','','','2017-07-08 17:16:24','2017-07-08 17:16:24','',0,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/?p=168',0,'post','',0),(169,1,'2017-07-08 16:18:54','2017-07-08 16:18:54','','Photograph about how Amelia Earhart ended up in the Marshall Islands surfaces_00','','inherit','closed','closed','','photograph-about-how-amelia-earhart-ended-up-in-the-marshall-islands-surfaces_00','','','2017-07-08 16:18:54','2017-07-08 16:18:54','',168,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Photograph-about-how-Amelia-Earhart-ended-up-in-the-Marshall-Islands-surfaces_00.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(170,1,'2017-07-08 16:18:57','2017-07-08 16:18:57','','Photograph about how Amelia Earhart ended up in the Marshall Islands surfaces_01','','inherit','closed','closed','','photograph-about-how-amelia-earhart-ended-up-in-the-marshall-islands-surfaces_01','','','2017-07-08 16:18:57','2017-07-08 16:18:57','',168,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Photograph-about-how-Amelia-Earhart-ended-up-in-the-Marshall-Islands-surfaces_01.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(171,1,'2017-07-08 16:19:35','2017-07-08 16:19:35','<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hold your horses and forget everything you knew about Amelia Earhart’s disappearance in 1937. A new photograph has emerged and it could suggest Earhart and navigator Fred Noonan survived their plane crash and ended up in the Marshall Islands.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-170\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Photograph-about-how-Amelia-Earhart-ended-up-in-the-Marshall-Islands-surfaces_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The photo, obtained from the National Archives by a retired federal agent named Les Kinney, shows a woman with a strong resemblance to Earhart, sitting with her back to the camera. There’s also a man in the leftmost side of the photo who is believed to be Noonan. Along with Earhart and Noonan, there are also a couple of local citizens in a dock with a Japanese vessel in the background.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\