. At the same time, the entire supporting cast exhibited a strong performance, especially Michael Keaton’s Adrian Toomes, or the Vulture.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-166\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Is-The-New-Spiderman-Movie-Any-Good_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">All in all, Spiderman: Homecoming takes everyone’s expectations and launches it to the stars. This is mainly because of a compelling plot, brilliant performances, and its amazing ties to the MCU.</h4>','Is The New Spiderman Movie Any Good?','','inherit','closed','closed','','164-revision-v1','','','2017-07-08 16:20:29','2017-07-08 16:20:29','',164,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/164-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(173,1,'2017-07-08 16:20:56','2017-07-08 16:20:56','<h4>Have you ever started your day without coffee? We imagine it’s horrible. Not only do you feel incomplete without caffeine in your body, you also seem to lack the energy needed to accomplish event the most mundane of tasks. On the other end of things, you feel like you can take on the world once you’ve had your coffee fix. But be careful though. You should know what your coffee limit should be.</h4>\r\n<h4><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/How-Much-Coffee-Should-Be-Enough-for-a-Day1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"555\" /></h4>\r\n<h4>According to experts, 4 cups of coffee each day is enough. You see, too much coffee exerts your brain and overworks it in the short-term. If you do this every day, you can expect to suffer long-term effects because of coffee overload. Some of these effects are restlessness, irritability, anxiety, insomnia, and irregular heartbeat.</h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>Do remember to regulate your coffee intake folk. Too much of something is always a bad idea, no matter how it is ingrained to your daily lives.</h4>','How Much Coffee Should Be Enough for a Day?','','inherit','closed','closed','','156-revision-v1','','','2017-07-08 16:20:56','2017-07-08 16:20:56','',156,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/156-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(174,1,'2017-07-08 16:22:59','2017-07-08 16:22:59','<h4>It’s not uncommon to enter a household and see a dog vying for your attention. It’s also common to see other homes with cats as their pet. But do the math and you’ll find out more homeowners prefer to take care of dogs instead of cats. Why is this the case?</h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>Well, dogs provide more security for people because they can hinder any criminals from causing you harm. They are brave and can pose an immediate danger to these unwanted people. On the other hand, cats will just run away at the first sight of a burglar.</h4>\r\n<h4><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-129\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Why-Most-People-Prefer-Dogs-Over-Cats1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></h4>\r\n<h4>Furthermore, dogs are more affectionate and can easily be trained than cats. They can easily learn new tricks and are more effective in making more people happy than cats do.</h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>This is not saying cats are a lesser kind of pet than dogs. In fact, the best way to summarize this is each person will always have a choice when it comes to their choice of pets. It just so happens more people choose dogs.</h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-130\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Why-Most-People-Prefer-Dogs-Over-Cats0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1100\" height=\"672\" />','Why Most People Prefer Dogs Over Cats','','inherit','closed','closed','','150-revision-v1','','','2017-07-08 16:22:59','2017-07-08 16:22:59','',150,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/150-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(175,1,'2017-07-08 16:28:41','2017-07-08 16:28:41','{\n    \"nav_menu_item[-3808743874864558000]\": {\n        \"value\": {\n            \"object_id\": 11,\n            \"object\": \"category\",\n            \"menu_item_parent\": 0,\n            \"position\": 4,\n            \"type\": \"taxonomy\",\n            \"title\": \"Fun\",\n            \"url\": \"http://www.noblebuzz.com/category/fun/\",\n            \"target\": \"\",\n            \"attr_title\": \"\",\n            \"description\": \"\",\n            \"classes\": \"\",\n            \"xfn\": \"\",\n            \"status\": \"publish\",\n            \"original_title\": \"Fun\",\n            \"nav_menu_term_id\": 4,\n            \"_invalid\": false,\n            \"type_label\": \"Category\"\n        },\n        \"type\": \"nav_menu_item\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','99b2a604-dc93-4437-a8d3-bb46dfa568c7','','','2017-07-08 16:28:41','2017-07-08 16:28:41','',0,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/99b2a604-dc93-4437-a8d3-bb46dfa568c7/',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(176,1,'2017-07-08 16:28:41','2017-07-08 16:28:41',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','176','','','2017-07-08 16:37:20','2017-07-08 16:37:20','',0,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/176/',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(177,1,'2017-07-08 16:29:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\n    \"show_on_front\": {\n        \"value\": \"page\",\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    }\n}','','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','69337bb2-c630-4f7a-9d3e-ecbbe0ff6fde','','','2017-07-08 16:29:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/?p=177',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(178,1,'2017-07-08 17:16:24','2017-07-08 17:16:24','<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hold your horses and forget everything you knew about Amelia Earhart’s disappearance in 1937. A new photograph has emerged and it could suggest Earhart and navigator Fred Noonan survived their plane crash and ended up in the Marshall Islands.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-170\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Photograph-about-how-Amelia-Earhart-ended-up-in-the-Marshall-Islands-surfaces_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The photo, obtained from the National Archives by a retired federal agent named Les Kinney, shows a woman with a strong resemblance to Earhart, sitting with her back to the camera. There’s also a man in the leftmost side of the photo who is believed to be Noonan. Along with Earhart and Noonan, there are also a couple of local citizens in a dock with a Japanese vessel in the background.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-169\" src=\"http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Photograph-about-how-Amelia-Earhart-ended-up-in-the-Marshall-Islands-surfaces_00.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a documentary about this new discovery, Forensic analyst Kent Gibson confirmed that the Japanese ship is the Koshu Maru, an army vessel. He also said that the man and woman in the photo exhibit strong features of Earhart and Noonan.</h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"Body\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">If confirmed, this changes a lot about how these two disappeared during the late 30s.</h4>','Photograph about how Amelia Earhart ended up in the Marshall Islands surfaces','','inherit','closed','closed','','168-revision-v1','','','2017-07-08 17:16:24','2017-07-08 17:16:24','',168,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/168-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(179,1,'2017-07-08 18:42:24','2017-07-08 18:42:24','<h4><span style=\"color: #000000;\">It\'s good to know it\'s not only us invisible people who struggle with weight, though: celebrities do too. Have a look at this incredible slideshow of celebrities who used to be fat before they took drastic action.</span></h4>\r\n<strong>Chris Pratt</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Another Hollywood hunk, who would\'ve guessed that Pratt used to be very boy-next-door. At his </span>heaviest<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> he weighed 280 </span>pounds,<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> and was told he was too heavy for a role in the film <em>Moneyball</em>. Dedicated Chris immediately worked on his weight transformation, and when he sent a photo of his new look to the film\'s director, he got the part. Hard work always pays off in the end.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1492\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/22Chris-Pratt.jpg\" alt=\"22chris-pratt\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Oprah Winfrey</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">The expert advice-giver loves her carbs. At her heaviest, Oprah weighed 237 pounds. These days she\'s a member of Weight Watchers and now weighs around 160 pounds. Looking fabulous, Oprah.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1482\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/12Oprah-Winfrey.jpg\" alt=\"12oprah-winfrey\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Tom Arnold</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Comedian Tom, who is married to Roseanne (yes, <em>that</em> Roseanne), lost one hundred pounds by cutting carbs and going to the gym. He\'s shrunk!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1493\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/23Tom-Arnold1.jpg\" alt=\"23tom-arnold1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Kelly Obsbourne</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelly is like marmite. You either love her or hate her. I think we can all agree that she looks miles better in the second </span>picture<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> though. It\'s not just the weight: her unflattering hairstyle and ghoulish makeup are </span>a disastrous.<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> She looks much prettier with the long blonde locks and bombshell red lips. She truly does look like a different person. From goth pig to classic Hollywood: amazing!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1505\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/35Kelly-Osbourne1.jpg\" alt=\"35kelly-osbourne1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Ronnie Ortiz</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Best known as one of the cast members of MTV\'s<em> Jersey Shore</em>, Ronnie Ortiz is famous for his beefy build and hot temper. Like Tyra Banks, Ortiz\'s appearance ranges from flabby to buff. Sometimes he has a beer belly, sometimes he has a six-pack. I think we all agree that we much prefer the buff version, eh ladies?</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1481\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/11Ronnie-Ortiz.jpg\" alt=\"11ronnie-ortiz\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Kevin Liles</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">From Michelin man to miniature man, this hip-hop expert was told by his doctor in 2007 that he needed to lose some weight. Going by the pictures, the diet certainly worked! His transformation is amazing, but at least he still has his trademark smile.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1486\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/16Kevin-Liles.jpg\" alt=\"16kevin-liles\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Aretha Franklin</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">What a transformation! Soulful </span>Arethra<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> looks much more like a natural woman now: respect! As you can see, she went from pudding to glam queen. At her </span>heaviest<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> she was a whopping 300 pounds and had family and friends fretting about her health. Thankfully, she took their advice and looks all the better for it.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1477\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/6Aretha-Franklin.jpg\" alt=\"6aretha-franklin\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Jerry Ferrara</strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">It\'s remarkable what even a small amount of weight loss does for the structure of the face. Ferrara, who plays Turtle on the HBO comedy series <em>Entourage</em>, lost more than fifty pounds during his transformation. Bravo!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1490\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/20Jerry-Ferrara.jpg\" alt=\"20jerry-ferrara\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Angie Stone</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Best known for being a member of the 70s hip-hop trio <em>The Sequence</em>, Angie Stone has lost over 75 pounds after being diagnosed with diabetes. Sometimes it takes a crisis to give us the push we need. You go, girl.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1507\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/38Angie-Stone.jpg\" alt=\"38angie-stone\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Wendy Williams</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Holy smokes! Look at Wendy\'s minuscule waist in the second pic! A television presenter by trade, this </span>daytime<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> TV celebrity has immensely lost weight, over fifty pounds dropped thanks to daily trips to the gym and cutting out junk food.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1491\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/21Wendy-Williams.jpg\" alt=\"21wendy-williams\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Christian Bale</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Christian Bale isn\'t afraid to take extreme measures for movie roles. He bulked up and became super-muscly for his role in <em>Reign of Fire</em>, then shed 70 pounds for <em>The Machinist</em>. If that\'s not enough, he muscled up again for <em>Batman Begins</em>, and then gained 50 pounds for <em>American Hustle</em>. His poor body must be wondering what the heck is going on. Well, you can\'t say he isn\'t dedicated.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1480\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/9Christian-Bale.jpg\" alt=\"9christian-bale\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Ricky Gervais</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Resident funny-man and face behind the original UK series <em>The Office</em>, Ricky decided he was sick of being fat and lazy and lost forty pounds. He hasn\'t lost his funny face, either. </span>Good man<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Ricky.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1494\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/24Ricky-Gervais1.jpg\" alt=\"24ricky-gervais1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Kim Kardashian</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kim needs no introduction. At her </span>heaviest<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> she was 200 pounds. After shedding her baby weight, Kim is currently back down to around 130 pounds. Incredible weight loss. Phew!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1497\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/27Kim-Kardashian.jpg\" alt=\"27kim-kardashian\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Chaz Bono</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sonny and Cher\'s daughter-turned-son (yes, Chaz is transgender) dropped 85 pounds when he joined the cast of <em>Dancing with the Stars</em>. Meat, fruit, nuts, and vegetables were the staples of his life-changing diet.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1499\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/29Chaz-Bono.jpg\" alt=\"29chaz-bono\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Rosie O\'Donnell</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Known more nowadays for her public </span>beefs<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> than her acting prowess, O\'Donnell looks amazing after she underwent gastric surgery. This resulted in her losing 175 pounds! Despite the fact that gastric surgery is controversial, O\'Donnell says it\'s the best decision she ever made.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1501\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/31Rosie-O-Donnell.jpg\" alt=\"31rosie-o-donnell\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Alec Baldwin</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">There have been times when Alec has been overweight. After finding out he was pre-diabetic, Baldwin quickly took back control of his health and lost an impressive forty pounds in the process.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1498\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/28Alec-Baldwin.jpg\" alt=\"28alec-baldwin\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Kirstie Alley</strong></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kirstie is a household name, thanks to her role in <em>Cheers as </em>Rebecca Howe. Over the years her weight has </span>yo-yo<span style=\"color: #000000;\">. At her </span>heaviest<span style=\"color: #000000;\">, she was 228 pounds, but since losing over 50 pounds she\'s back to looking her best.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1502\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/32Kirstie-Alley.jpg\" alt=\"32kirstie-alley\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Mariah Carey</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">After giving birth to twins in 2011, Carey gained 70 pounds of baby weight. These days, she\'s still rocking those unique curves, even after separating from her husband Nick Cannon in 2014.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1504\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/34Mariah-Carey.jpg\" alt=\"34mariah-carey\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Nicole \'Snooki\' Polizzi</strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Another reality TV personality, Snooki battled anorexia as a teenager. At only 4 ft 8 inches, even a little bit of weight drowns her tiny frame. Now she weighs only 99 pounds, even after having two kids. As long as she\'s not being too obsessive about it, her weight loss is a great thing. She was never seriously </span>obese<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> though, so be careful not to overdo it Snooki!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1515\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/47Nicole-Snooki-Polizzi.jpg\" alt=\"47nicole-snooki-polizzi\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Star Jones</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Best known for appearing on <em>The View</em>, Star was at one point morbidly obese, weighing over 300 pounds. Over the course of three years, she lost more than half her body weights, Jones eventually admitted to having gastric surgery after insisting that her drastic weight loss was the result of a diet.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1523\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Star-Jones1.jpg\" alt=\"star-jones1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Chaka Khan</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Wowza! What a difference. The queen of funk, who has sold over 70 million albums and won 10 Grammy awards, looks striking after her weight loss. She lost sixty pounds by going on a vegan diet and joining a gym.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1496\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/26Chaka-Khan.jpg\" alt=\"26chaka-khan\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Shonda Rhimes</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Rhimes is best known as the writer behind the TV series <em>Grey\'s Anatomy</em>. She has lost over 127 pounds and was inspired to lose weight once she realized she could no longer buckle her seatbelt! Smart woman: safety over comfort-eating. You go, girl.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1508\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/39Shonda-Rhimes1.jpg\" alt=\"39shonda-rhimes1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Austin \'Chumlee\' Russell</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Star of the history channel\'s reality series <em>Pawn Stars</em>, Chumlee is a firm favorite. He weighed 320 pounds and started to think seriously about his weight after his father\'s death in 2009. So far he has managed to lose an impressive 75 pounds, thanks to the support of his girlfriend Tanya.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1516\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/48Chumlee.jpg\" alt=\"48chumlee\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Graham Elliot</strong></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Just look at the difference here! Another celebrity foodie, poor Graham couldn\'t resist dipping into his own goodies. At one point he weighed over 400 pounds! Thankfully, he had surgery to drop the pounds and now weighs around 200 pounds.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1509\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/41Graham-Elliot.jpg\" alt=\"41graham-elliot\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Raven Symone</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">That cute little face is unforgettable. Do you remember the cute little girl on <em>The Cosby Show</em> who made us all laugh with her cheekiness? That was Raven. In 2003 Disney gave her an entire show called <em>That\'s So Raven</em> where she became an idol for teens the world over. It\'s clear from these pictures that the pressures of fame caused her to temporarily munch on a burger too many, but thankfully she </span>loe<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> weight and now looks slim and absolutely radiant. A girl-next-door at heart, Raven admits she cheats on her diet sometimes. See? Celebs are just like the rest of us<strong>!</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1479\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/8Raven-Symone.jpg\" alt=\"8raven-symone\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></strong></span><strong>Jordin Sparks</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jordin was only 15 when she hypnotized viewers with the beautiful tonal quality of her singing on <em>American Idol</em>. Since her time on the show, she\'s one of the few who has truly established herself as a solo artist. She was a healthy, curvaceous teenager back then. Nowadays, she\'s slimmed down by fifty pounds and looks slender on the red carpet.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1511\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/43Jordin-Sparks.jpg\" alt=\"43jordin-sparks\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Ricki Lake</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Poor Ricki has battled with depression as well as her weight. She weighed 260 pounds at her heaviest. Since taking the reins and battling to lose weight, she\'s looking much healthier and happier.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1514\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/46Ricki-Lake1.jpg\" alt=\"46ricki-lake1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Jennifer Hudson</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jennifer Hudson is another celebrity who became famous after appearing on <em>American Idol</em>. A lady with a big voice, Hudson also has been known to have a big body. But just look at her now: what a stunner.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1506\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/36Jennifer-Hudson.jpg\" alt=\"36jennifer-hudson\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Mama June </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">The<em> Here Comes Honey Boo Boo</em> star underwent a series of weight loss and plastic surgeries and documented it in a reality TV series. The first episode aired just recently, so you\'ll only see the end results if you tune in!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1517\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/50Mama-June.jpg\" alt=\"50mama-june\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong>Paul Wall</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Texas-style rapper Paul Wall is another celebrity who lost a startling amount of weight. In 2010 he made a red carpet appearance that astounded the world. He used to weigh 320 pounds and now weighs only 200 thanks to gastric surgery and the support of his wife.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1510\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/42Paul-Wall.jpg\" alt=\"42paul-wall\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Randy Jackson</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Everyone\'s favorite <em>American Idol</em> host (well, mine anyway) hasn\'t always been the slimmest of celebrities. In the first </span>picture<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> you can see how wide Randy\'s frame is. Like Rosie O\'Donnell, he opted for gastric surgery and dropped an astounding 130 pounds. He\'s half the man he used to be!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1503\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/33Randy-Jackson.jpg\" alt=\"33randy-jackson\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Gabourey Sidibe </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Most actors and actresses have to do bit parts and badly-written films for a long time before they hit the big-time, but not Gabourey Sidibe. The lucky duck landed a starring role in the film <em>Precious</em>. This was her first ever try at acting! Not only that, but she earned an Academy Award nomination for the performance she gave! Her transformation may not be as extreme as some of the other celebrities on the list, but Gabourey is steadily losing weight and looking fabulous!</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1518\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/51Gabourey-Sidibe.jpg\" alt=\"51gabourey-sidibe\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n\r\n<strong>Tyra Banks</strong>\r\n\r\nTyra Banks is one of those lucky few who looks beautiful no matter what size she is. She\'s never been really, really obese, but her weight often goes up and down like a yo-yo. Sometimes she\'s curvy with a good proportion of extra meat; other times she\'s almost waif-like. Her background in the world of modeling, which is very harsh when it comes to naturally curvy women, is probably why Banks struggles to maintain her weight. We\'re all cheering her on anyway, because she\'s beautiful even when she has an extra bulge or two.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1524\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Tyra-Banksff.jpg\" alt=\"tyra-banksff\" width=\"722\" height=\"494\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>50 Cent</strong>\r\n\r\nHoly smokes! This is one of those rare times when the fatter version looks better. 50 Cent looks suave and healthy in the first pic. The second one is horrific. Maybe he\'s been spending too much time in \'da club? Turns out his extreme look was for the movie <em>Things Fall Apart</em>. Phew! He even won a Grammy for his role as Deon, so maybe the liquid diet he consumed to reach his target weight was worth it. Still, he looks positively ghostly.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1476\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5-50-Cent.jpg\" alt=\"5-50-cent\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Jonah Hill</strong>\r\n\r\nWho would\'ve guessed? Behind that pudgy face, Jonah Hill is a hottie! Hill was inspired by Brad Pitt to shed some weight when they worked together on <em>Moneyball</em> for his upcoming role in <em>21 Jump Street</em>. Whoever said peer pressure is a bad thing obviously never had weight issues.<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1513\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/45Jonah-Hill1.jpg\" alt=\"45jonah-hill1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>Dr. Dre</strong>\r\n\r\nGangster rapper extraordinaire, Dr. Dre transformed from flabby face to toned body-builder. Can you believe he\'s 51 years old?<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1487\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/17Dr-Dre.jpg\" alt=\"17dr-dre\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Perez Hilton</strong>\r\n\r\nYes, that\'s right: our favorite celebrity gossiper who loves to tell us about juicy scandals used to look very different to how he does now. Look at the first picture! Hilton certainly wouldn\'t look out of place ordering the family-sized meal at Burger King.  Good old Hilton didn\'t fall prey to any diet fads in order to go from monstrous to skinny. He did things the old-fashioned way: he ate the recommended, healthy amount, and exercised regularly. It took him four years to lose the weight, so it\'s obvious he didn\'t cut any corners. Keep it up, Perez!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1522\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Perez-Hilton.jpg\" alt=\"perez-hilton\" width=\"722\" height=\"468\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Seth Rogen</strong>\r\n\r\nSince his breakthrough role in <em>The 40-Year-Old Virgin</em>, Seth has become known as one of the funniest actors in Hollywood. He lost around fifty pounds for his leading role in <em>The Green Hornet</em>. Only time will tell if his transformation is permanent, though. Rogen loves junk food and isn\'t very active. He gained ten pounds again immediately after filming ended!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1483\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/13Seth-Rogen.jpg\" alt=\"13seth-rogen\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Click \'next\' to see a game show host who changed his lifestyle after having heart surgery<!--nextpage--></strong><strong>Drew Carey</strong>\r\n\r\nSome people are disciplined enough to lose weight when they see the pounds piling on. For Drew Carey, however, it took heart surgery and a diabetes diagnosis to make him see that his weight problem was...a problem! His inspiration for changing his ways was his nine-year-old son Connor. It isn\'t easy to stick to a healthy diet, but luckily for Drew he was motivated by the thought of being in his son\'s life until a ripe old age. And who says kids are a nuisance? Kids can also be life-savers!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1474\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/2Drew-Carey.jpg\" alt=\"2drew-carey\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Christina Aguilera</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n\r\nWell, at least we know that getting fat doesn\'t mean you can\'t sing. Christina was still belting out unbelievably high notes even when she was at her biggest. Over the years, she has received a lot of press about her fluctuating weight and contradictory looks. She\'s been the blonde, blue-eyed teen queen, the black-haired gothic goddess, the Spanish seductress, and many more. One thing is clear: Aguilera does her own thing, even if there\'s a big media fuss over it. The diva reigns supreme!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1489\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/19Christina-Aguilera.jpg\" alt=\"19christina-aguilera\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>John Goodman</strong>\r\n\r\nWow! Would you look at that! There\'s a sharp contrast in the two pictures here. Not only has John Goodman lost a ton of weight, he also looks more sleek and well-put-together in the second picture. Some celebrities are recognizable to us as their fatter version; Goodman included. He first graced our screens as the likable husband Dan on the TV sitcom <em>Roseanne </em>looking much more like the person in the first picture than the second. His skinny self barely looks like the same person, but he looks great!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1475\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/4John-Goodman.jpg\" alt=\"4john-goodman\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Janet Jackson</strong>\r\n\r\nI have to admit, if I was one of the Jackson\'s I\'d probably have issues too. The entire family is a circus of eccentrics, and having a baby brother who goes on to be twenty times more famous that the Jackson Five ever doesn\'t help. Poor Janet tried the music route, but her songs never had the appeal of Michael\'s. It must be difficult to be unmemorable, so it\'s no surprise that the sister-in-the-shadows struggles with her weight. Rest in peace Michael Jackson, the world\'s greatest pop star. Poor, poor Janet.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1519\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Janet-Jackson1.jpg\" alt=\"janet-jackson1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Zach Galifianakis</strong>\r\n\r\nNot only does Zach have a surname that\'s impossible to pronounce, he also has a history of being overweight. You can see by the tell-tale belly bulge in the first pic that Zach enjoyed a McDonalds or two. But let\'s be realistic: he wouldn\'t have made us laugh as much in <em>The Hangover</em> without his endearing pudgy face. Sometimes chubby guys make the best comedians. Hopefully he has other job offers though, because now he\'s all handsome and serious looking. He looks more like a drama actor than a comedy one now, but at least his health is all the better for it!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1488\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/18Zach-Galifianakis.jpg\" alt=\"18zach-galifianakis\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Lauren Alaina</strong>\r\n\r\nLauren stunned us on <em>American Idol</em> with her sultry country voice. Since her time on the show, she lost 25 pounds and looks incredible. Hopefully her new look will help her career, particularly because she came second to another country singer, the low-voiced Scottie. Good luck Lauren, and don\'t overdo the slimming just to get more column inches!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1520\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Lauren-Alaina1.jpg\" alt=\"lauren-alaina1\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Ruben Studdard</strong>\r\n\r\nRuben won the 2<sup>nd</sup> season of <em>American Idol</em>. The 6 foot 3 inches tall singer is known for his gospel, pop and R&amp;B tracks. He publicly acknowledged wanting to lose weight by going on the TV show <em>Biggest Loser</em>, and lost over a hundred pounds! Fantastic!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1478\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/7Ruben-Studdard.jpg\" alt=\"7ruben-studdard\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage--><strong>Al Roker</strong>\r\n\r\nWeekday weather anchor Al Roker opted for gastric surgery and has lost a total of 140 pounds since going through the procedure. Things are looking sunny for Al!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1512\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/44Al-Roker1.jpg\" alt=\"44al-roker1\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n\r\n<strong>Abby Lee Miller</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Cruella Deville of the Lifetime network, Abby is the unforgettable dance coach on <em>Dance Moms</em>. Not even the most pushy mom messes with Abby. After her own mother was hospitalized, Abby made the plunge to lose pounds and dropped numerous dress sizes. Good, because I often found it strange to see an overweight dance coach. Kudos to Abby, and may it continue.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1495\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/25Abby-Lee-Miller.jpg\" alt=\"25abby-lee-miller\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Click next to see the unbelievable weight transformation of an Australian comedienne<!--nextpage--></strong><strong>Rebel Wilson</strong>\r\n\r\nThis actress and stand-up comedian from Australia is 37, and has come a long way since starting her weight loss regime. She never felt like being bigger was an obstacle in her career, and notes how she was signed to her agent partially due to her different look! Don\'t become too skinny, Rebel, or you\'ll be just another slim blonde beauty. Be proud of those wonderful curves!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1521\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/MTI0ODUyMzgwODE3Njk3NDEx1.jpg\" alt=\"mti0oduymzgwode3njk3ndex1\" width=\"759\" height=\"561\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>Carrie Fisher</strong>\r\n\r\nThe actress best known for her role as Princess Leia struggled with a number of issues for many years including bipolar disorder. For the 2015 <em>Star Wars</em> remake, Fisher decided that enough was enough. She started taking regular medication for her mental disorder, exercised with a personal trainer, and changed her diet. Not only does she look better; she\'s in a better place in her head too.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1484\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/14Carrie-Fisher.jpg\" alt=\"14carrie-fisher\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage--><strong>Queen Latifah</strong>\r\n\r\nHip-hop artist and actress Queen Latifah shed some weight in order to set a better example for her female fans.  She was a surprise feature on the red carpet after losing more than thirty pounds.  She says she loves her curves more than ever.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1500\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/30Queen-Latifah.jpg\" alt=\"30queen-latifah\" width=\"728\" height=\"485\" />','Celebrities Who Have Undergone Gastric Sleeve Surgery','','publish','closed','closed','','celebrities-who-have-undergone-gastric-sleeve-surgery','','','2017-07-08 18:42:24','2017-07-08 18:42:24','',0,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/?p=179',0,'post','',0),(180,1,'2017-07-08 18:39:09','2017-07-08 18:39:09','','2Drew-Carey','','inherit','closed','closed','','2drew-carey','','','2017-07-08 18:39:09','2017-07-08 18:39:09','',179,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2Drew-Carey.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(181,1,'2017-07-08 18:39:11','2017-07-08 18:39:11','','4John-Goodman','','inherit','closed','closed','','4john-goodman','','','2017-07-08 18:39:11','2017-07-08 18:39:11','',179,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/4John-Goodman.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(182,1,'2017-07-08 18:39:11','2017-07-08 18:39:11','','5-50-Cent','','inherit','closed','closed','','5-50-cent','','','2017-07-08 18:39:11','2017-07-08 18:39:11','',179,'http://www.noblebuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-50-Cent.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(183,1,'2017-07-08 18:39:12','2017-07-08 18:39:12','',